title: The King of Kung Fu (1978) A deadly tower. Five masters. One impossible mission.

sources.title: The King of Kung Fu (1978) A deadly tower. Five masters. One impossible mission.
sources.description:
A priceless document that would enable the invasion of China falls into the hands of a ruthless man.
The document is hidden at the top of a tower, and to reach it, one must overcome 6 deadly trials. Only one man is capable: Wang (Bruce Le).
Japanese, Germans, and traitors now clash in a merciless battle to seize the plans...
